episodes.title: Alleged cult leader called himself ‘ladies’ man,’ said he had no need to rape women in recording
episodes.description:
There was more disturbing testimony Monday from an alleged cult leader who is on trial for rape in DeKalb County. He told police in a recording that he was a “ladies’ man” and that the allegations against him were false, but a former follower told a much different story.
